You cultivate cane previously?

975
01:24:08,961 --> 01:24:10,133
没有 先生 我没种过
No, sir, I have not.

976
01:24:10,295 --> 01:24:12,468
你的动作很纯熟
It comes to you quite naturally.

977
01:24:12,631 --> 01:24:13,632
你受过教育?
Are you educated?

978
01:24:14,299 --> 01:24:17,678
没有 先生 黑奴是来干活的 不是来读书写字的
No, sir. Niggers are hired to work, not read or write.

979
01:24:19,513 --> 01:24:21,140
你会拉小提琴
You play the fiddle.

980
01:24:21,640 --> 01:24:23,438
是的 先生 我会拉
Yes, sir. Yes, I do.

981
01:24:24,810 --> 01:24:26,983
威拉德・亚纳 河上游的一个种植园主...
Willard Yarner, a planter up the bayou...

982
