三周后要庆祝他的结婚纪念日
celebrates his anniversary in three weeks' time.

983
01:24:30,607 --> 01:24:32,860
我会把你的名字报给他
I'll hold out your name to him.

984
01:24:33,026 --> 01:24:35,620
你赚的就自己收着吧
What you earn is yours to keep.

985
01:24:36,280 --> 01:24:37,372
