带他们出去 挨鞭子吧
Take them out, get to whipping.

1036
01:29:36,913 --> 01:29:38,961
真是个悲剧
It's a tragedy.

1037
01:29:40,083 --> 01:29:41,835
这一切怎么会发生?
How does such come to pass?

1038
01:29:42,836 --> 01:29:46,056
卑贱地在地里干活 采摘棉花
Working a field and picking cotton like a lowly hand.

1039
01:29:46,590 --> 01:29:48,968
我的地位也就高那么一点点 
I'm of a damn sight better station.

1040
01:29:50,010 --> 01:29:52,104
你知道 我是个监工
I worked as an overseer, you know.

1041
01:29:52,262 --> 01:29:53,684
我不知道 先生
I did not know, sir.

1042
01:29:53,847 --> 01:29:55,349
别用"先生"
Not "sir."

1043
01:29:56,016 --> 01:29:57,859
喊我"阿姆斯比"
Just "Armsby."

1044
01:29:58,727 --> 01:30:00,900
我欠他的 不比你们中的任何一人多
I'm not owed more than any other in the field.

1045
01:30:01,062 --> 01:30:04,032
那你怎么会来这里的 如果你不介意我这么问?
How did you arrive at such a place, if I may ask?

1046
01:30:04,441 --> 01:30:07,035
别这么正式 我们只是聊聊天而已
Ask, it's just conversation.

1047
01:30:09,154 --> 01:30:12,124
我那会有点嗜酒...
I became a little too dependent on the whiskey...

1048
01:30:12,282 --> 01:30:14,751
对工作很不上心
a little too undependable on the job.

1049
01:30:15,994 --> 01:30:18,793
听着 在你骂我酒鬼之前...
Now, before you say I'm just a sorry drunkard...

1050
01:30:18,955 --> 01:30:21,083
让我把话讲完
let me state my case.

1051
01:30:22,000 --> 01:30:24,128
像监工这种稳定的活
As reliable employment as overseeing is,

1052
01:30:24,252 --> 01:30:26,346
其实是对精神上的折磨
it is no easy chore on the spirit.

1053
01:30:27,172 --> 01:30:30,016
我的意思是 任何一个有良知的人...
I say, no man of conscious...

1054
01:30:30,175 --> 01:30:32,644
都会因天天抽打他人...
can take the lash to another human day in and day out...

1055
01:30:32,802 --> 01:30:35,180
使得自己内心饱受折磨
without shredding at his own self.

1056
01:30:36,181 --> 01:30:38,354
时间久了...
Takes him to a place...

1057
01:30:38,516 --> 01:30:43,022
他要么为了保持心智 不断为自己找借口...
where he either makes excuses within his mind to be unaffected...

1058
01:30:43,521 --> 01:30:46,866
要么寻求某种方式惩罚自己的罪孽
or he finds some way to trample his guilty sensations.

1059
01:30:47,776 --> 01:30:49,369
所以 我选择惩罚自己
So, I trampled.

1060
01:30:49,527 --> 01:30:51,450
不断地惩罚
With frequency.

1061
01:30:52,989 --> 01:30:56,118
我沉迷于财富的传说
I gave in to tales of wealth and prosperity.

1062
01:30:59,371 --> 01:31:03,877
但高额的利润却都涌进种植园主人们的口袋里
But such profitable outcomes are reserved for plantation masters.

1063
01:31:04,501 --> 01:31:07,675
而我们其余的人只能任劳任怨
It's the lot of the rest of us to serve.

1064
01:31:09,297 --> 01:31:14,679
现在 我只想拿份体面地收入然后回家
Now, all I want is to earn a decent wage and get myself home.

1065
01:31:46,876 --> 01:31:48,970
我日复一日的劳作
The proceeds of my fiddling performances.

1066
01:31:49,796 --> 01:31:53,926
只挣了这么一点 但这是我的所有了
Just a few picayunes, but all I have in the world.

1067
01:31:54,551 --> 01:31:57,930
如果你能帮帮我 我就把这些全部都给你
I promise them to you if you will do me the favor I require.

1068
01:31:58,096 --> 01:32:02,146
但我请求你 如果你做不到 不要把我供出来 
But I beg you not to expose me if you cannot grant the request.

1069
01:32:02,684 --> 01:32:03,776
嗯...
Uh...

1070
01:32:04,477 --> 01:32:06,104
你想要我做什么?
What is it you ask?

1071
01:32:06,271 --> 01:32:08,444
首先 你得保证 先生
First, your word, sir.

1072
01:32:09,149 --> 01:32:10,150
我以我的名誉担保
On my honor.

1073
01:32:12,277 --> 01:32:14,279
我的请求很简单
It's a simple enough request.

1074
01:32:15,655 --> 01:32:17,453
我只需要你去一趟马克思维的邮局
I only ask that you deposit a letter

1075
01:32:17,574 --> 01:32:19,326
帮我寄一封信...
at the post office in Marksville...

1076
01:32:19,492 --> 01:32:22,962
然后永远保守这个秘密
and that you keep the action an inviolable secret forever.

1077
01:32:26,166 --> 01:32:28,635
先生 请庇护我
A patron is what I require, sir.

1078
01:32:35,175 --> 01:32:36,017
我会的
I'll do it.

1079
01:32:37,135 --> 01:32:39,558
我会接受你给我的报酬 无论多少
And I'll accept whatever payment's offered.

1080
01:32:42,307 --> 01:32:44,856
为了帮你 我让自己陷于危险之中
To assist you, I put my own self at risk.

1081
01:32:45,643 --> 01:32:47,486
但我还会这么做...
I will do so...

1082
01:32:47,645 --> 01:32:50,819
只要求有些合理的补偿
but fair compensation is all I ask.

1083
01:33:00,325 --> 01:33:02,248
写好你的信
Draw up your letter.

1084
01:33:02,410 --> 01:33:04,879
我们两天后见?
We'll meet again in two days?

1085
01:33:06,581 --> 01:33:08,379
好 两天后
In two days.

1086
01:33:11,169 --> 01:33:12,671
谢谢
Thank you.

1087
01:34:30,290 --> 01:34:32,088
听着 伙计...
Well, boy...

1088
01:34:32,250 --> 01:34:37,097
我听说我有个识字的黑奴 他不但会写信
I understand I got a learned nigger that writes letters.

1089
01:34:38,173 --> 01:34:41,268
还想找个白人帮他寄信来着
Tries to get white fellas to mail them.

1090
01:34:47,599 --> 01:34:50,273
阿姆斯比今天告诉我的...
Armsby told me today...

1091
01:34:50,435 --> 01:34:52,938
魔鬼在我的黑奴中作祟
the devil was among my niggers.

1092
01:34:54,606 --> 01:34:57,576
我尤其需要盯着其中的某位...
That I had one that needed watching...

1093
01:34:57,734 --> 01:35:00,078
不然他就会逃跑
or he would run away.

1094
01:35:02,030 --> 01:35:03,907
我问他为什么...
When I asked him why...

1095
01:35:04,782 --> 01:35:08,286
他告诉我你去找他...
he said you come over to him...

1096
01:35:08,453 --> 01:35:11,297
半夜把他叫醒...
waked him up in the middle of the night...

1097
01:35:11,456 --> 01:35:14,130
求他去马克思维那边...
and wanted him to carry a letter...

1098
01:35:15,376 --> 01:35:17,128
帮你寄封信
to Marksville.

1099
01:35:22,217 --> 01:35:24,640
