1277
01:47:39,203 --> 01:47:41,046
比这的任何一个男人都多
More than any man here.

1278
01:47:41,205 --> 01:47:43,299
有了这个 我会变得干净
And for that, I will be clean.

1279
01:47:43,457 --> 01:47:45,175
这就是我唯一的要求
That's all I ask.

1280
01:47:45,334 --> 01:47:48,383
我会去肖老爷的种植园就是为了这个
This, here, what I went to Shaw's for.

1281
01:47:49,838 --> 01:47:50,885
骗子
Liar.

1282
01:47:51,048 --> 01:47:54,643
上帝见证 真的是这样!
The Lord knows that's all!

1283
01:47:54,802 --> 01:47:55,724
你是个骗子
You're a liar.

1284
01:47:55,886 --> 01:47:59,311
而你 被你自己的贪婪蒙蔽!
And you, blind with your own covetousness!

1285
01:48:00,182 --> 01:48:02,310
我没有说谎 主人
I don't lie, Master.

1286
01:48:02,810 --> 01:48:06,064
如果你要杀了我 我也会坚持这么说
If you kill me, I'll stick to that.

1287
01:48:06,814 --> 01:48:08,407
看来我得好好教训你一顿
I'll fetch you down.

1288
01:48:09,233 --> 01:48:11,281
让你知道去肖那里的下场
I'll learn you to go to Shaw's.

1289
01:48:11,735 --> 01:48:12,827
特里奇
Treach.

1290
01:48:14,863 --> 01:48:16,365
去取绳子来
Run and fetch some line.

1291
01:48:16,532 --> 01:48:17,704
爱德华!
Edward!

1292
01:48:19,326 --> 01:48:22,330
把她衣服扒了 绑到树桩上给我狠狠地打
Strip her. Strike her bare and lash her to the post.

1293
01:48:40,764 --> 01:48:42,908
这是你自找的 小茜
You done this to yourself, Pats.

1294
01:48:54,611 --> 01:48:55,783
打啊
Do it.

1295
01:49:00,868 --> 01:49:03,087
把她往死里打
Strike the life from her.

1296
01:49:09,293 --> 01:49:10,715
你来打
Beat her.

1297
01:49:12,337 --> 01:49:14,590
让她尝尝鞭子的味道! 让她如愿以偿!
Give her the whip! Give it all to her!

1298
01:49:15,883 --> 01:49:18,853
普莱特 你过来 现在你来打她
Platt, you come here and you beat her now.

1299
01:49:21,305 --> 01:49:22,397
普莱特!
Platt!

1300
01:49:25,184 --> 01:49:26,436
过来!
Come here!

1301
01:49:28,187 --> 01:49:30,360
我宁愿由你来打 普莱特!
I'd rather it you, Platt!

1302
01:49:31,315 --> 01:49:33,067
你来打她
You strike her.

1303
01:49:33,942 --> 01:49:35,364
打她啊
Strike her.

1304
01:49:57,674 --> 01:49:59,267
他就没用劲
He pantomimes.

1305
01:49:59,885 --> 01:50:02,308
她身上几乎没有鞭痕
There's barely a welt on her.

1306
01:50:02,763 --> 01:50:05,141
这就是你的黑鬼...
That's what your niggers make of you...

1307
01:50:05,307 --> 01:50:07,480
把你当傻子一样愚弄
a fool for the taking.

1308
01:50:11,980 --> 01:50:14,403
打她 普莱特 打她啊!
Strike her, Platt. Strike her!

1309
01:50:31,125 --> 01:50:32,547
你给我好好地打
You will strike her.

1310
01:50:32,709 --> 01:50:34,427
你要打得她皮开肉绽
You will strike her until her flesh

1311
01:50:34,545 --> 01:50:36,263
血肉模糊...
is rent and meat and blood flow equal...

1312
01:50:36,421 --> 01:50:39,220
否则我看见一个黑奴 就杀一个
or I will kill every nigger in my sight.

1313
01:50:39,383 --> 01:50:40,885
你听懂了吗?
You understand me?

1314
01:50:41,051 --> 01:50:43,895
打她! 打她!
Strike her! Strike her!

1315
01:51:27,139 --> 01:51:29,938
我还没喊停呢 我说停你才能停!
Until I say no more. I ain't said nothing!

1316
01:51:39,860 --> 01:51:41,157
把鞭子给我!
Give me the whip!

1317
01:51:42,154 --> 01:51:43,371
起来!
Get up!

1318
01:52:02,799 --> 01:52:04,472
你这个魔鬼!
Thou devil!

1319
01:52:07,012 --> 01:52:08,559
总有一天...
Sooner or later...

1320
01:52:09,223 --> 01:52:11,817
善有善报 恶有恶报
somewhere in the course of eternal

1321
01:52:11,975 --> 01:52:14,569
总有一天你会遭报应的!
justice, thou shalt answer for this sin!

1322
01:52:19,983 --> 01:52:23,032
报应? 根本不会有报应
Sin? There is no sin.

1323
01:52:24,488 --> 01:52:27,412
人可以对他的财产为所欲为
Man does how he pleases with his property.

1324
01:52:33,038 --> 01:52:36,759
现在 普莱特 我现在心情已经很嗨
At the moment, Platt, I'm of great pleasure.

1325
01:52:36,917 --> 01:52:38,760
你他妈给我小心点 
You be goddamn careful I don't want to

1326
01:52:38,877 --> 01:52:40,675
别再火上浇油
come and lighten my mood no further.

1327
01:54:58,975 --> 01:55:00,477
巴斯老爷
Master Bass.

1328
01:55:00,769 --> 01:55:03,943
请问您来自这个国家的哪个地方
I want to ask you what part of the country you come from.

1329
01:55:05,148 --> 01:55:07,025
我不是这个国家的
No part of this land.

1330
01:55:08,110 --> 01:55:10,158
我来自加拿大
I originate from Canada.

1331
01:55:11,154 --> 01:55:12,701
来 猜猜它在哪里
Now, guess where that is.

1332
01:55:12,864 --> 01:55:14,787
我知道加拿大在哪
I know where Canada is.

1333
01:55:15,617 --> 01:55:17,369
我自己去过那儿
I've been there myself.

1334
01:55:22,290 --> 01:55:24,133
蒙特利尔...
Montreal...

1335
01:55:24,292 --> 01:55:27,341
金斯顿 昆士顿 还有很多的地方
and Kingston and Queenston and a great many places.

1336
01:55:27,504 --> 01:55:29,347
对一个黑奴来说算阅历丰富了
Well-traveled for a slave.

1337
01:55:29,506 --> 01:55:30,553
你怎么来这的?
How came you here?

1338
01:55:32,634 --> 01:55:34,307
巴斯老爷...
Master Bass...

1339
01:55:36,638 --> 01:55:40,017
如果正义能够得以伸张 我怎么会到这来
if justice had been done, I never would have been here.

1340
01:55:44,813 --> 01:55:46,156
此话怎讲?
How's this?

1341
01:55:47,190 --> 01:55:48,237
告诉我
Tell me all.

1342
01:55:53,697 --> 01:55:55,870
我不敢告诉您
I'm afraid to tell you.

1343
01:55:57,534 --> 01:56:00,663
你所说的每一个字都会被严格保密
Every word you speak is a profound secret.

1344
01:56:08,211 --> 01:56:09,884
你的故事...
Your story...

1345
01:56:10,547 --> 01:56:12,015
真令人大吃一惊
it is amazing.

1346
01:56:12,174 --> 01:56:14,176
却很可悲
And in no good way.

1347
01:56:18,930 --> 01:56:22,560
您相信正义吗 先生 就像您所说的?
Do you believe, sir, in justice, as you said?

1348
01:56:23,727 --> 01:56:25,274
相信
I do.

1349
01:56:25,437 --> 01:56:29,237
您相信奴隶制是邪恶的并且应被彻底废除吗?
That slavery is an evil that should befall none?

1350
01:56:32,068 --> 01:56:33,866
我认为是的
I believe so.

1351
01:56:34,029 --> 01:56:35,952
若你真是如此...
If you truly do...

1352
01:56:37,741 --> 01:56:40,790
那么我请求你 我恳求你...
then I ask, I beg...

1353
01:56:43,455 --> 01:56:46,254
写封信给我在北方的朋友...
that you write my friends in the north...

1354
01:56:46,625 --> 01:56:49,424
让他们了解到我的处境...
acquainting them of my situation...

1355
01:56:50,795 --> 01:56:55,096
并且恳求他们证明我是自由的身份
and beseeching them to forward free papers.

1356
01:57:00,096 --> 01:57:01,769
重新见到我的妻子...
It would be...

1357
01:57:04,768 --> 01:57:07,612
和我的家人...
an unspeakable happiness...

1358
01:57:09,231 --> 01:57:11,279
那将是...
to see my wife...

1359
01:57:13,777 --> 01:57:16,075
无法言表的幸福
and my family again.

1360
01:57:21,952 --> 01:57:25,331
我来到这个国家20年了...
I traveled this country for the best part of 20 years...

1361
01:57:25,997 --> 01:57:28,921
我的自由就是一切
and my freedom is everything.

1362
01:57:29,084 --> 01:57:33,430
明天能离开这里 是我最高兴的事情
The fact that I can walk out of here tomorrow brings me great pleasure.

1363
01:57:36,049 --> 01:57:38,302
我的命对任何人都没有多大意义
My life doesn't mean much to anyone.

1364
01:57:39,636 --> 01:57:43,311
但看起来你的命对许多人都意义重大
It seems yours might mean a lot to a whole lot of people.

1365
01:57:45,058 --> 01:57:49,529
但是你的请求 令我害怕
But what you ask of me, sir, scares me.

1366
01:57:51,690 --> 01:57:54,534
我不得不说 我害怕
And I must say, I am afraid.

1367
01:57:55,652 --> 01:57:57,996
不仅仅是为你 还是为我
Not just for you, but for me.

1368
01:58:07,163 --> 01:58:09,336
我会为你写信的 先生
I will write your letter, sir.

1369
01:58:09,780 --> 01:58:11,101
而且如果它能为你带来自由
And if it brings you your freedom,

1370
01:58:11,126 --> 01:58:12,366
那不仅仅会是我的荣幸
it will be more than a pleasure.

1371
01:58:12,377 --> 01:58:14,345
那将会是我的责任
It will have been my duty.

1372
01:58:14,504 --> 01:58:17,508
现在 你可以把那些木片递给我吗?
Now, would you kindly hand me those shingles?

1373
02:00:52,078 --> 02:00:53,250
普莱特!
Platt!

1374
02:00:53,663 --> 02:00:55,711
叫普莱特的家伙在哪?
Where's the boy called Platt?

1375
02:00:59,002 --> 02:01:00,379
过来
Come here, boy.

1376
02:01:22,525 --> 02:01:24,277
你叫普莱特 对吗?
Your name is Platt, is it?

1377
02:01:26,070 --> 02:01:27,367
是的 先生
Yes, sir.

1378
02:01:28,031 --> 02:01:29,578
你认识那个人吗?
You know that man?

1379
02:01:47,383 --> 02:01:48,976
帕克先生
Mr. Parker.

1380
02:01:49,636 --> 02:01:51,138
再说一遍?
Say again?

1381
02:01:53,181 --> 02:01:55,024
帕克先生
Mr. Parker.

1382
02:01:55,475 --> 02:01:58,149
那位先生收到了一封充满着许多指控的信
That man received a letter compiling many accusations.

1383
02:01:58,311 --> 02:02:00,154
你看着我的眼睛...
You look me in the eye...

1384
02:02:00,814 --> 02:02:02,540
并且无论如何 请你如实地回答我
and on your life, you answer me truthfully.

1385
02:02:02,565 --> 02:02:04,238
除了普莱特你还有其他名字吗?
Have you any other name than Platt?

1386
02:02:04,400 --> 02:02:06,402
所罗门・诺瑟普是我的名字
Solomon Northup is my name.

1387
02:02:06,569 --> 02:02:07,769
治安官 这是怎么回事?
Sheriff, what's all this?

1388
02:02:07,904 --> 02:02:09,281
这是公事
It's official business.

1389
02:02:09,447 --> 02:02:10,744
我的黑奴 就是我的事
My nigger, my business.

1390
02:02:10,907 --> 02:02:12,534
你的事可以等
Your business waits.

1391
02:02:12,700 --> 02:02:13,792
跟我说说你的家庭
Tell me of your family.

1392
02:02:14,118 --> 02:02:15,540
我有一位妻子 两个孩子
I have a wife, two children.

1393
02:02:15,703 --> 02:02:16,579
这他妈什么情况?
What the hell?

1394
02:02:16,704 --> 02:02:18,515
- 你孩子的姓名?  - 玛格丽特和阿朗佐
- What are your children's names?  - Margaret and Alonzo.

1395
02:02:18,540 --> 02:02:19,891
你妻子结婚前叫什么?
What was your wife's name before her marriage?

1396
02:02:19,916 --> 02:02:21,418
叫安妮・汉普顿 我就是你们要找的人
Anne Hampton. I am who I say.

1397
02:02:21,584 --> 02:02:22,585
你去哪 普莱特?
Where you going, Platt?

1398
02:02:23,461 --> 02:02:25,381
谁授权你干涉我的财产了?
Who authorized you to interfere with my property?

1399
02:02:25,505 --> 02:02:26,597
这是我的权力
My authority.

1400
02:02:26,756 --> 02:02:28,099
普莱特 你回来 普莱特!
Platt, you come back here. Platt!

1401
02:02:28,800 --> 02:02:29,926
小子 你回来 
You come back here, boy.

1402
02:02:30,927 --> 02:02:32,099
孩子
Boy.

1403
02:02:34,556 --> 02:02:36,979
你放开他 普莱特是我的黑奴!
You unhand him. Platt is my nigger!

1404
02:02:37,141 --> 02:02:38,563
他是所罗门・诺瑟普先生
He is Mr. Solomon Northup.

1405
02:02:38,726 --> 02:02:39,602
你瞎说
You say.

1406
02:02:39,769 --> 02:02:42,238
你到这儿来 和我不熟 还要来抢我的人
You come here, unfamiliar to me, and make claims.

1407
02:02:42,397 --> 02:02:44,123
毫无疑问 这位先生就是所罗门・诺瑟普
I got no doubts. The man is Solomon Northup.

1408
02:02:44,148 --> 02:02:46,492
他是个鬼! 他是我的黑奴 我会为他跟你死磕到底!
The hell he is! He's my nigger, and I'll fight you for him!

1409
02:02:46,651 --> 02:02:47,948
你有你的权利
As is your right.

1410
02:02:48,111 --> 02:02:50,312
我也有我的权利 而且我也很乐意在法庭上让你倾家荡产
As it will be my pleasure to bankrupt you in the courts.

1411
02:02:50,446 --> 02:02:52,790
你自己决定 放开他
Your decision. Unhand him.

1412
02:02:53,573 --> 02:02:55,134
我知道这件事你也有份 普莱特
I know you had some hand in this, Platt.

1413
02:02:55,159 --> 02:02:56,627
我会弄个水落石出的
I'm gonna get to the bottom of it.

1414
02:02:56,786 --> 02:02:57,912
别理他
Pay him no mind.

1415
02:02:58,079 --> 02:02:59,456
我为这个黑奴付了大价钱
I paid good money for this nigger.

1416
02:02:59,581 --> 02:03:00,958
法院的文件可以证明这一点!
Courthouse got papers to prove it!

1417
02:03:01,124 --> 02:03:02,922
我们也有文件证明他是自由的!
And we got papers proving he's free!

1418
02:03:03,084 --> 02:03:04,802
你是我的 你是属于我的 你听见了吗 普莱特?
I own you. You belong to me. You hear me, Platt?

1419
02:03:04,961 --> 02:03:06,087
放开他!
Unhand him!

1420
02:03:06,254 --> 02:03:08,473
日落之前 你的背上会再添200个伤口的!
You'll have 200 stripes across your back by sundown!

1421
02:03:08,631 --> 02:03:09,757
普莱特!
Platt!

1422
02:03:09,966 --> 02:03:11,809
把我的马牵来 特里奇
Get my horse, Treach.

1423
02:03:20,935 --> 02:03:22,152
离他远点 小茜
Get away from him, Pats.

1424
02:03:23,479 --> 02:03:25,322
我很快就会见到你的
I'm gonna be seeing you real soon.

1425
02:03:25,481 --> 02:03:27,449
所罗门 我们得快点
Solomon, we need to make haste.

1426
02:03:29,152 --> 02:03:30,153
不
No.

1427
02:03:30,737 --> 02:03:32,080
快 所罗门
Solomon.

1428
02:05:09,002 --> 02:05:11,175
我会道歉...
I'll apologize...

1429
02:05:13,256 --> 02:05:15,258
为我的出现道歉
for my appearance.

1430
02:05:17,844 --> 02:05:19,767
但过去的这些年里...
But I have had...

1431
02:05:20,722 --> 02:05:22,690
我经历了...
a difficult time...

1432
02:05:23,683 --> 02:05:26,402
一段艰难的岁月
these past several years.

1433
02:05:31,274 --> 02:05:32,617
玛格丽特
Margaret.

1434
02:05:38,197 --> 02:05:39,915
阿朗佐
Alonzo.

1435
02:06:11,064 --> 02:06:12,782
他是谁?
Who is this?

1436
02:06:13,816 --> 02:06:15,818
他是我的丈夫
He's my husband.

1437
02:06:17,320 --> 02:06:18,492
丈夫
Husband.

1438
02:06:19,322 --> 02:06:22,667
很高兴见到你 先生
It is very good to meet you, sir.

1439
02:06:24,452 --> 02:06:26,671
我们还有很多需要互相了解
We have much acquainting to do.

1440
02:06:26,829 --> 02:06:28,172
是的 先生
Yes, sir.

1441
02:06:29,415 --> 02:06:33,465
然后这是你的外孙
And this is your grandson.

1442
02:06:34,295 --> 02:06:37,469
他叫所罗门・诺瑟普・斯汤顿
Solomon Northup Staunton.

1443
02:06:47,683 --> 02:06:49,276
所罗门
Solomon.

1444
02:06:55,525 --> 02:06:56,822
安妮...
Anne...

1445
02:06:59,195 --> 02:07:00,993
原谅我
forgive me.

1446
02:07:04,534 --> 02:07:08,038
没有什么要原谅的
There is nothing to forgive.

1447
02:07:30,134 --> 02:07:36,438
所罗门・诺瑟普是为数不多的
摆脱奴隶身份重获自由的绑架受害者之一

1448
02:07:37,634 --> 02:07:42,338
